  "title": "BIM Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and create detailed Revit models to support architectural design and project requirements</li><li>Update BIM models to ensure compliance with applicable codes and regulations, maintaining accuracy and quality</li><li>Assist in coordinating BIM-related tasks and detailing to facilitate seamless project execution</li><li>Support the continuous improvement of office BIM standards and procedures</li><li>Collaborate effectively within project teams and teamwork to meet project goals</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of experience in BIM modelling</li><li>Proficient in Autodesk Revit, Archicad, and Autocad software</li><li>Knowledgeable in relevant codes and regulations</li><li>Ability to work independently and as a team player</li></ul>",
